Readme

A note

I have only included the open-ended questions in this report. To begin with, we just have the word clouds. This dashboard has both Translated and Raw word clouds. Translation was completed using the google translate API and only the top 200 most frequently words per question were translated using an in-house, smart and cost saving translation mechanism. The raw word clouds have been added for Sharan to look at.
